MM8DTiny - Software for MM8D growing house controlling device
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. About software
-----------------
  It is a tiny version of MM8D software for control MM6D and MM7D devices
  with v0.3 or later software. This version of software uses external
  program for get data from controllers via HTTP access.

  It does not include SSH access, web interface, logging and debug
  operation mode and the control does not calculate the outside temperature.

Requirements:

  DOS version:
    Hardware:    AT or newer computer,
                 80386 or newer processor,
                 NIC.
    Software:    FreeDOS,
                 Packet driver for NIC,
                 GNU Wget.

  Linux version:
    Hardware:    AT or newer computer,
                 80386 or newer processor,
                 NIC.
    Software:    GNU/Linux OS,
                 GNU Wget.

2. How to get installer package for my OS?
------------------------------------------
a. Visit homepage (see later) to download installer packages:

  DOS:           MM8DTY01.ZIP
  Linux:         mm8dtiny-0.1-i386.tar.gz

  (This packages contents GNU Wget.)

b. Download from Github

  > git clone https://github.com/pozsarzs/mm8dtiny.git

3. How to set the program?
--------------------------
  Edit MM8DTINY.INI and CHANNELS\ENV-CH?.INI files.

